g.text: change. Higher temperatures have dried vegetation to produce fuel and concurrent drying of
groundwater accelerates combustion. Physicians should note the impact of global warming on
human health with regard to fires and heatwaves so they can be attuned to relevant medical
conditions and can proactively help their patients.
